t directly infect humans, risks still exist after some unpredictable mutations. Thus, this study increased our understanding of the genetic diversity and transmission of SARSr-CoVs carried by bats in the field.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Li, Linmiao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhang, Libiao", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhou, Jiabin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "He, Xiangyang", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yu, Yepin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Liu, Ping", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Huang, Wenzhong", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Xiang, Zuofu", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Jinping", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chang, Yung-Fu", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/2e76316c8490252e26da0b20703eea67", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/5eba96f3e849bf8f3138c2276ca9f2f5f68b6c0d314706b1a024870dc6e0b5de", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZLJKQCS2", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZLJKQCS2", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/87df3c56b8fa7aa704a3326b4f9043bf!/b9919-12371", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "e00463-22", "title": "mBio", "volume": "13"}, "alternate_ident